  <section class="page-hero">
    <div class="container">
      <h1>Storytime</h1>
      <p>Beloved read-alouds and forest stories shared with Norbert by my side</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ====== INTRO + VIDEO GRID ====== -->
  <section class="section" style="background: var(--cream);">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="text-center fade-in" style="margin-bottom: 2.5rem; max-width: 700px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;">
        <p style="font-size: 1.1rem; line-height: 1.8;">These are the stories I have read and shared with Norbert by my side. Some became beloved favorites, some helped shape the enchanted forest, and some carried so much heart that viewers immediately wanted to hold them as books. Together, they form the storytime path that opened this whole world.</p>
        <p style="font-size: 1.1rem; line-height: 1.8;">Here you will find gentle read-alouds, luminous forest tales, and comforting stories made to be felt. Whether you are a parent, a grandparent, a teacher, or simply someone who needs a softer place to land, I hope these stories bring a little light to your day.</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="video-grid-full">

        <div class="media-card fade-in">
          <div class="card-body">
            <h3>The Tug of War Lesson</h3>
            <p>The original storytime video that inspired the book and first showed how deeply this work connected.</p>
            <div class="ig-embed-wrapper">
              <blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/reel/DC-WhaBMzdj/" data-instgrm-version="14" style="background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:540px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%;"></blockquote>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="media-card fade-in">
          <div class="card-body">
            <h3>A Tale of Illuminating Love</h3>
            <p>A standout favorite, filled with warmth, tenderness, and the kind of light that stays with you.</p>
            <div class="ig-embed-wrapper">
              <blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/reel/DJFjIZiSeer/" data-instgrm-version="14" style="background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:540px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%;"></blockquote>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="media-card fade-in">
          <div class="card-body">
            <h3>Song of the Still Stars</h3>
            <p>A soft and luminous read-aloud that invites wonder, quiet, and heart-centered listening.</p>
            <div class="ig-embed-wrapper">
              <blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/reel/DItVmxdsa1i/" data-instgrm-version="14" style="background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:540px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%;"></blockquote>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="media-card fade-in">
          <div class="card-body">
            <h3>The Forest That Remembers</h3>
            <p>A gentle forest tale rooted in memory, meaning, and the feeling that love remains.</p>
            <div class="ig-embed-wrapper">
              <blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/reel/DUZeigvkpFb/" data-instgrm-version="14" style="background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:540px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%;"></blockquote>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="media-card fade-in">
          <div class="card-body">
            <h3>Norbert and Lyra in the Quiet Night</h3>
            <p>A story of stillness, presence, and the gentle magic of being together when the world goes quiet.</p>
            <div class="ig-embed-wrapper">
              <blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/reel/DTRRd7yDcTh/" data-instgrm-version="14" style="background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:540px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%;"></blockquote>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="media-card fade-in">
          <div class="card-body">
            <h3>Norbert and Lyra's Christmas Heart Lights</h3>
            <p>A seasonal storytime offering filled with warmth, comfort, and the simple magic of being together.</p>
            <div class="ig-embed-wrapper">
              <blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/reel/DSqdhE_kp9H/" data-instgrm-version="14" style="background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:540px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%;"></blockquote>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>
